    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnacione eius millesimo centesimo quadragesimo
                        secundo, die octavo mensis februarii, indictione quinta, in <placeName
                            ref="#places/3595">Capite Gauri</placeName>. Petivi a te domno <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3747">Paulo</persName> venerabili <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Shores #Sea #Penalty #Fish #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Ports #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName ref="#places/4179"
                                >Pomposie</placeName></orgName>, consensu monachorum, mihi
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus Schoine">Petro Schoine</name></persName>
                        meisque liberis et heredibus atque detinere voluerimus per pactum, concedis
                        nobis medietatem unius <rs key="#Shores">litoris maris</rs> a <rs
                            key="#Ports">portu</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Shores #Sea #Penalty #Fish #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Ports"
                            ref="#places/3596">
                            <geogName
                                key="#Shores #Sea #Penalty #Fish #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Ports"
                                >Gauri</geogName></placeName> usque ad portum <placeName
                            key="#Shores #Sea #Penalty #Fish #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Ports">
                            <geogName
                                key="#Shores #Sea #Penalty #Fish #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Ports"
                                ref="#estates/2465">Volane</geogName></placeName>; abendum,
                        tenendum, piscandum, super reditu quem vobis redere debeamus omni anno <rs
                            key="#Fish #Rent_in_kind">pisces marinos capitaneos centum</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Rent_in_money">duas libros</rs> pro pensione; conservare,
                        adinplere firmiter tenere promitto vobis, sup pene <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                            uncias duas</rs>, firma permaneat. Ego <persName key="#Notary">
                            <name ref="Hughicio Pomposianus">Ugizo</name></persName> Pomposiane <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scripsi ec. Petivi a te domno Paulo abbate,
                        consensu monachorum, mihi <persName><name ref="Deusdedit"
                            >Deodato</name></persName> meisque liberis et heredibus concedis mihi
                        quartam partem litoris maris a Gauro usque ad Volana; piscandum, tenendum
                        quicquid ibi in eodem litore et mari ad utilitatem artis predicte facere
                        voluerimus, reddere vobis omni anno in Quadragesima maiore <rs
                            key="#Fish #Rent_in_kind">quinquaginta pisces marinos capitaneos</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Rent_in_money">libram unam</rs> pro pensione, adducta omnia
                        per nos in monasterio vestro. <rs key="#Penalty">Auri unciam unam</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
